  "detailed_description": "<h1>WISHLIST NOW!</h1><p><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1734070/extras/d607e4a0017a9c5c1448ee78b3a68bd3.avif?t=1741302317\" width=616 height=146 /></span></p><br><h1>About the Game</h1><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><picture><source srcset=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1734070/extras/e4e12385fcc3cd9f13d97c3ddad7461f.apng?t=1741302317\"><img src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1734070/extras/e4e12385fcc3cd9f13d97c3ddad7461f.poster.avif?t=1741302317\" class=\"bb_img\" width=566 height=99 /></picture></span><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" >The Scarlet Devil Mansion, which has become an endless dungeon!</h2>The Scarlet Devil Mansion is a dungeon that changes its appearance every time you enter it, thanks to Sakuya Izayoi's ability.<br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1734070/extras/44d92a6ed42361d0cee21f3d4e981cd2.poster.avif?t=1741302317\" width=574 height=218 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1734070/extras/44d92a6ed42361d0cee21f3d4e981cd2.webm?t=1741302317\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1734070/extras/44d92a6ed42361d0cee21f3d4e981cd2.mp4?t=1741302317\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" >More than 20 different characters!</h2>Take on the game with your favorite character!<br>Playable characters in the Early Access version<br>Hakurei Reimu,Kirisame Marisa,Rumia,Cirno,Konpaku Youmu,Fujiwarano Mokou,Hong Meirin,Patchouli Knowledge,Izayoi Sakuya,Remilia Scarlet,Flandre Scarlet<br>Other characters will be added in future updates.<br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1734070/extras/6fa83bb91f2d33903e00a79cdae06a2a.poster.avif?t=1741302317\" width=574 height=218 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1734070/extras/6fa83bb91f2d33903e00a79cdae06a2a.webm?t=1741302317\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1734070/extras/6fa83bb91f2d33903e00a79cdae06a2a.mp4?t=1741302317\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" >Strengthen your character by collecting items!</h2>Build your ideal style with the high-tempo reinforcement system and abundant items!<br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1734070/extras/31b595c2757059f91562eb6beb8a2f27.poster.avif?t=1741302317\" width=574 height=218 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1734070/extras/31b595c2757059f91562eb6beb8a2f27.webm?t=1741302317\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1734070/extras/31b595c2757059f91562eb6beb8a2f27.mp4?t=1741302317\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span><br><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><picture><source srcset=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1734070/extras/133369bee87482df4f1218a90ac656d9.apng?t=1741302317\"><img src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1734070/extras/133369bee87482df4f1218a90ac656d9.poster.avif?t=1741302317\" class=\"bb_img\" width=566 height=128 /></picture></span>",
